      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "At the beginning of each wave, the player must interact with the statue
    to begin the wave and fight the enemies. \nEach wand has a different effect on
    the enemy. The wands are randomised with an added bonus of damage after each
    wave. \n\nThe wands:\nFireball: Does burn damage to the enemy for 5 seconds.
    \nFrost: Slows down the enemy. \nLightning: Does damage to enemies within a radius
    of where the enemies are standing. \nNormal: Does normal damage to the enemies.
    (No special effects).  "
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
